-- BP Dividend Payment Is Challenged by Lawyers for Louisiana Fishermen
-- Laurel Brubaker Calkins
-- 2010-06-16T17:08:56Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/bp-dividend-payment-is-challenged-by-lawyers-for-louisiana-fishermen.html

          
          
             Lawyers representing commercial
fishermen in Louisiana asked a federal judge to stop BP Plc from
“dissipating assets,” including paying a dividend, to help
ensure the company is able to pay claims over the Gulf  
Oil spill.  
